snippet.textDisplay:
QB ...teri Lathe de chadar from Hamsafar to laal meri pat ...u have conquered our hearts...when u r in studio u r angel from the sky...
No matter how many khushbo ke jhonkey Farhan throws your way...we will not let u be alone...kiyun ke tere mera sath purana ai
...I just want to listen to...mere kan de jhumke...kiyun ke tere mera sath pura ai...
when u sing Punjabi songs it is as if u never left chenab and jhelum...
Farhan my friend u r great but u had no chance ...against qb 's  the lathe chadar...first time I have seen everybody is loose and seen Qb actually having fun...may be tinak dhin tinak...have infected everybody...
Shani tusi great ho...Vicaji...drummer ahad ...the whole team ...this has been hell of a ride ...this year...Coke studio Pakistan this annual heart check is essential for survival otherwise we will expire...Finally coke has shown the world what being a Pakistani always meant to rest of us the silent majority...love for all..ingenuity and hard work...let us  keep surprising  our friends...when we have QB, coke studio and Jawad Bashir...our future looks bright...
For now I am grabing my lathe de chadar ...w slatey rung ...going to let the pigeon  fly  ...w  msg of love to the land of my ancestors.
